

Share prices on the Colombo Stock Exchange closed up Tuesday with the key Colombo All Share Price Index rising 17.85 points to close at 2290.70 points.

On the other hand, the highly capitalized Milanka Price Index gained 6.15 points to close at 2934.35 points.

A total turnover of 241 million rupee (2.41 million US dollars) was recorded during the day with a volume of 12.51 million shares being traded.

